In particular, the requirements for the precise documentation of the procedure as well as for the marking, safe storage and confidentiality of the offers significantly restrict the possibility of manipulation, such as subsequent changes to the offers.
In addition, the officers responsible for opening the offers are not allowed to perform any other tasks in connection with the service to be awarded.
